3.01	Mehragan	Mehregan	Mehrgân (alternatively: Mihragān, Persian: ‎) or Jashn-e Mehregân festival celebrated since the pre-Islamic era to honor the Yazata of "Mehr" (Persian: ‎), which is responsible for friendship, affection and love. It is also widely referred to as Persian Festival of Autumn.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d3/Mehregan_Table_Persian_Festival_of_Autumn_in_Holland_Photo_by_Persian_Dutch_Network_2011.jpg/320px-Mehregan_Table_Persian_Festival_of_Autumn_in_Holland_Photo_by_Persian_Dutch_Network_2011.jpg
